---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import FAQSchema from '../../components/FAQSchema.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Tattoo Shop Inventory Management — Track Ink, Needles &amp; Supply Costs" description="InkFlow's tattoo inventory management tracks ink, needles, and supplies with low-stock alerts and cost-per-session tracking. Never run out mid-session. Start free." />
  <FAQSchema questions={[
    { question: "Can I set low-stock alerts?", answer: "Yes. Set minimum quantities per item. InkFlow notifies you when stock is running low — via email, SMS, or in-app." },
    { question: "Does it track cost per session?", answer: "Yes. Link inventory items to services. InkFlow calculates supply costs per appointment automatically." },
    { question: "Can multiple artists manage inventory?", answer: "Yes. Each artist can log usage. Studio owner sees consolidated inventory across all artists." },
  ]} />
  <Navbar />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3">TATTOO INVENTORY MANAGEMENT</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">Tattoo Shop Inventory Management: Track Supplies &amp; Cost Per Session</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400">InkFlow's inventory management tracks every supply — ink, needles, cartridges, and aftercare — with low-stock alerts and cost-per-session calculations. Never run out mid-session again.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Why Spreadsheets Fail for Tattoo Inventory</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Running out of supplies mid-session costs you money and credibility.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Nothing worse than realizing you're out of black ink during a lining session. InkFlow alerts you before you hit zero.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">You don't know which services are profitable and which aren't.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Without cost-per-session tracking, you're guessing at margins. InkFlow calculates supply costs per appointment automatically.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Multi-artist inventory is chaos without a system.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Each artist logs usage. Owner sees consolidated inventory across all artists. No more "who used the last bottle of X?"</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Inventory Features Built for Tattoo Studios</h2>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-16">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Real-Time Stock Tracking with Low-Stock Alerts</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Track every item — from ink bottles to needle cartridges — with automatic low-stock notifications before you run out.</p>
          <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Item-Level Tracking with Categories</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Organize by category: ink, needles, cartridges, aftercare, PPE. Each item has name, SKU, quantity, minimum threshold, and supplier.</p>
          <h5 class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">Alerts via SMS, Email, or In-App</h5>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Set minimum quantities per item. When stock drops below threshold, InkFlow notifies you before it's too late.</p>
          <h6 class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400">Barcode Scanning for Quick Check-In</h6>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Scan barcodes on supply shipments to auto-update inventory. No manual data entry for new stock.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Inventory dashboard]</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Cost per session]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Cost Per Session Shows Your Exact Margins</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Link inventory items to services. InkFlow calculates supply costs per appointment automatically.</p>
          <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Per-Appointment Profit Calculation</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">See revenue minus supply cost for every session. Know which services have the best margins.</p>
          <h5 class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">Vs Spreadsheets: Automatic vs Manual</h5>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Spreadsheets require manual entry after every session. InkFlow auto-calculates from service-linked inventory items.</p>
          <h6 class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400">Monthly P&amp;L Reports by Artist</h6>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Export monthly profit and loss by artist or by service. Know exactly how much each artist consumes in supplies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <!-- COMPARISON TABLE -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">InkFlow vs Spreadsheets vs POS: 8-Dimension Comparison</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-400">Most studios use spreadsheets or nothing. Here's how they compare for tattoo inventory management.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-700">
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-gray-400 font-medium">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400 font-semibold">InkFlow</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-500 font-medium">Spreadsheets</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 text-gray-500 font-medium">POS (Square)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Real-time stock tracking</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">Manual only</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">Basic retail</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Low-stock alerts</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Cost per session auto-calc</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Multi-artist tracking</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">Complex</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Barcode scanning</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✓</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Linked to booking data</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Monthly P&amp;L by artist</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">Manual</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Setup time</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">15 min</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">Hours</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">1-2 days</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Can I set low-stock alerts?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. Set minimum quantities per item. InkFlow notifies you when stock is running low — via email, SMS, or in-app.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Does it track cost per session?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. Link inventory items to services. InkFlow calculates supply costs per appointment automatically.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Can multiple artists manage inventory?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. Each artist can log usage. Studio owner sees consolidated inventory across all artists.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-white">Does InkFlow integrate with my supplier's ordering system?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Currently, InkFlow tracks inventory and alerts you when stock is low. We're building supplier integration for automatic reordering.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Never Run Out of Supplies Again</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">Free plan includes basic inventory tracking. Upgrade for low-stock alerts and cost-per-session reports.</p>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="/pricing" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">Compare plans</a></p>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
